# Copy to .env.local for local overrides (gitignored). Vite only exposes VITE_-prefixed
# vars to client code, and only at build time — see src/main.tsx.

# Error tracking. Leave blank to disable Sentry entirely (the default) — a plain `npm run
# build` works fine without a Sentry project. Get a DSN from sentry.io -> Settings ->
# Projects -> <project> -> Client Keys. DSNs are meant to be public (they identify where to
# send events, not a secret), so baking one into the browser bundle is expected practice.
VITE_SENTRY_DSN=
